    <node id="Chapter 3 Overview: Matching Your Ads to Your Marketing Strategy (list)">
      <data key="d0">Chapter 3 Overview: Matching Your Ads to Your Marketing Strategy (list)</data>
      <data key="d1">list</data>
      <data key="d2">This list outlines the key topics in Chapter 3, focusing on targeting advertising groups, setting geographic ranges, deciding campaign scope, and fulfilling marketing objectives through Facebook Ads. It introduces the main strategies for effective Facebook advertising, supporting the chapter's emphasis on leveraging Facebook's targeting capabilities.</data>
      <data key="d3">chunk-d5187f72b95adf4fda2d11bfe2eae46b</data>
      <data key="d4">Facebook Ad 60.pdf</data>
      <data key="d5">1773904716</data>
